        <div class="component-inner">

        <!-- Introduction -->
        <div class="component-introduction row justify-content-start text-left " data-os-animation="fadeIn" data-os-animation-delay="0s" data-os-animation-duration="1.2s">
            <div class="info col">

                

                    <div class="text base-text">
                        <p>City Council is comprised of a Mayor, 3 Regional Councillors and 3 City Councillors. The Mayor is elected by voters across the entire City, while the Regional and City Councillors are elected by voters in one of the 3 respective wards.</p>
<p>The Mayor and Regional Councillors sit on both the City Council and the Council of the Regional Municipality of Durham. The City Councillors sit on City Council only. The Mayor and all Councillors serve a 4 year term.</p>
<p>Members of Council are responsible for the management and administration of the City's resources.  As well as attending Council and Committee meetings, some members are also active on a number of board and committee meetings.</p>
<p>Please visit the <a rel="noopener" href="https://cityofpickering.maps.arcgis.com/apps/webappviewer/index.html?id=bcc7b2b014294afe8bae801656108087" target="_blank" title="open Ward Map in new window" class="    ">online map portal</a> to find out what ward you are in.</p>
                    </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!--// Introduction -->


                        <div class="component-main row listing  listing_basic-grid listing-pods " >
            <div class="item   items-2 col-12 item_text-below usn_pod_textimage    text-left  " data-os-animation="fadeIn" data-os-animation-delay="0s" data-os-animation-duration="1.2s">
